<paragraph id="963294A550C67C80B7F3A6BF54E5B977" pageId="8" pageNumber="9">The species epithet refers to the French macaroon cookie (&quot;macaron&quot; in the French language), which has a similar appearance to the articulated valves. The species epithet is proposed as a noun in apposition.</paragraph>
